GETAFFECTLONG
NAME
        GetAffectLong()

SYNOPSIS
        string GetAffectLong(object ob)

DESCRIPTION
        Adds a descriptive string to a creature's long desc indicating some variable information. In the case of LIB_BODY, it indicates wakefulness or intoxication. For LIB_CLAN, clan membership is indicated. The argument is not used.

EXAMPLES
         

LOCATION
        /lib/body
/lib/clan

SEE ALSO
         

Author
        Cratylus

